  <description>
    <p>
      Doom Runner is yet another launcher of ZDoom and derivatives with graphical user interface.
      It is written in C++ and Qt, and it is designed around the idea of presets for various multi-file
      modifications (Brutal Doom with mutators, Project Brutality with UDV, Complex Doom Clusterfuck, ...)
      to allow one-click switching between them and minimize any repetitive work.
    </p>
  </description>
